=<  ::  this lifecycle wrapper makes the arvo door
    ::  (multi-armed core) look like a gate (function
    ::  or single-armed core), to fit urbit's formal
    ::  lifecycle function.  a practical interpreter 
    ::  can ignore it.
    ::
    |=  {now/@da ovo/ovum}
    ~>  %slog.[0 leaf+"arvo-event"]
    .(+> +:(poke now ovo))
