    ::
    =>  ?~  lul.job  .
        %=    .
           lul.mal  ~&  [%lull-boot `@p`(mug u.lul.job)]
                     (slap !>(..arms) (ream u.lul.job))
        ==
    ::  upgrade %zuse, vane shared libraries
    ::
    =>  ?~  zus.job  .
        %=    .
